# Severance knowledge (agent reference)

Read [`.cursor/knowledge/severance-facts.md`](../knowledge/severance-facts.md), [`.cursor/knowledge/show-app-continuity.md`](../knowledge/show-app-continuity.md), and [`.cursor/knowledge/visual-direction.md`](../knowledge/visual-direction.md) before changing copy, ambient events, MDR visuals, or Lumon branding. For habit math, also read [`.cursor/knowledge/engine-design.md`](../knowledge/engine-design.md).

**Voice rules**
- Clinical corporate handbook tone; short imperative lines
- Prefer: refinement, compliance, department, Board, workstation, file, quota, temper
- Avoid: generic “habit tracker,” “pet,” gamey “level up,” purple cyber neon
- Easter eggs = lore crumbs; CR/XP rewards stay tiny

**Visual rules**
- MDR = scary numbers, temper quadrants (WO/FC/DR/MA), phosphor CRT; terminal = header + center stage + bins 01–05 + edge vitals (see visual-direction)
- Office = sage carpet, white panels, ceiling grid, 4-pod desks
- Ambient stays rare (hours-scale), not arcade
